<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-461] remove support for format for magic byte 0 in 0.8</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-461</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Since 0.8 is a non-backward compatible release, should we remove the support for magic byte 0 in Message and support only magic byte 1?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
